sentences: Harold Ha (Korean: 하원택; born March 16, 1982), better known as Bizniz (Korean: 비즈니즈), is a South Korean rapper and singer signed to Brand New Music.
He debuted as a member of Korean hip hop group Infinite Flow in 1999, and he released his first solo EP, This Is Bizniz, in 2008.
